{
  "name": "RPlog_The_Alderaan",
  "title": "A Major's Report and a Ghost from the Past",
  "summary": "Aboard the New Republic vessel Alderaan, newly promoted Major Jessalyn reports to Admiral Jeralic on the bridge, securing permission for a Casparian ship's crew to dispose of rancid fuel and flagging that Colonel Skywalker has returned with a boy bearing useful intelligence. Jeralic follows her to the crew quarters, where the disguised street musician Shenner -- passing as a young man -- nervously explains that her employer, Grathix Stur'ttrakath, is searching for General Solo and that Imperials have grown too interested in her. The briefing turns up the name of an Imperial Lady, Alora Antieres, from a datacard Shenner surrenders, and Jeralic orders Skeezix to pull NRI files on Alora, the Lord Sabbath, and Palanhi. Running beneath the official talk, Jessalyn trades flustered whispers with her friend Avalyne, who teases out the major's hopeless infatuation with Luke Skywalker, while the arrival and abrupt removal of a man named Quick visibly rattles Jessalyn. The session ends with Jeralic tasking Jessalyn to escort Shenner to the comm room to contact her boss.",
